    Copy your program from the previous exercise and make the following modifications:

       * Change function to draw a hexagon instead of a triangle (the turn angle is 60)
       * Change the name of the drawTriangle function to drawHexagon
       * Make your program draw a row of 3 triangles each with side length 40

